{"tid":321050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行換鎖工人被困提款機　收據口遞紙仔求救","createTime":"2017-07-14T03:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T09:35:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":398,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94c20f6879f837a718d0b195292748ce41403134","tid":321050,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1499977493_2f8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1499977493_2f8b.jpg&h=9f7cb09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人被困珀斯克里斯蒂市這間美國銀行分行的ATM內，只好遞紙條向顧客求救。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n「提款機是人扮的」這個笑話已經講了很久，但美國德州這部提款機內真的有人。一名外判工人在換鎖時被困在提款機房內，他卻沒有帶手機，只好從提款機收據口遞紙條出去，跟顧客求救。<br />\n<br />\n事發於科珀斯克里斯蒂市（Corpus Christi）一間美國銀行（Bank of America）分行。顧客收到的其中一張紙條寫道，「請救我。我被困在此。我沒有帶手機。請打給我老闆」，然後附上了一個電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n有些顧客以為這是個惡作劇，幸好有人打電話報警，警員到場踢開門才救他出來，當時他已經被困兩小時。<br />\n<br />\n去救人的警員奧爾登（Richard Olden）也忍不住笑說：「我們聽到機器裏面傳出一點小聲音。你人生再也不會見到這樣的事了，某個人被困在ATM機內。太瘋狂了。」"},{"pid":"78bc64a0d76e447daec1439c0b032443b13f1865","tid":321050,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170714&amp;guid=56953666&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170714%26guid%3D56953666%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=674nXqZdAHT%2BHRUkGxEGD26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3e60d530\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170714%26guid%3D56953666%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=d7e66505\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170714&amp;guid=56953666&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"f087b95c5ce14e12961885198c1845a261f9434f","tid":3210